@startuml UC_ManagePromotions_Sequence
title Manage Promotions

actor "Owner / Manager" as ManagerUser

participant "Web Client" as WebClient
participant "Promotion Management Service" as PromoService

ManagerUser -> WebClient: open promotions dashboard
WebClient -> PromoService: request coupons and memberships
PromoService --> WebClient: coupon list and membership list
WebClient --> ManagerUser: show promotions dashboard

ManagerUser -> WebClient: open coupon form
ManagerUser -> WebClient: enter coupon conditions and discount policy
WebClient -> PromoService: send coupon data
PromoService --> WebClient: confirm coupon saved
WebClient --> ManagerUser: refresh coupon list

ManagerUser -> WebClient: change coupon status (activate or deactivate)
WebClient -> PromoService: send coupon status update
PromoService --> WebClient: updated coupon information
WebClient --> ManagerUser: update coupon row

ManagerUser -> WebClient: open membership settings
WebClient -> PromoService: request membership rules
PromoService --> WebClient: membership list
WebClient --> ManagerUser: show membership settings

ManagerUser -> WebClient: modify membership rules
WebClient -> PromoService: send updated membership rules
PromoService --> WebClient: confirm membership rules saved
WebClient --> ManagerUser: show updated membership settings

@enduml
